---
title: (Vegetarian) Golden Haloumi & Roasted Pumpkin with Rocket Salad & Dukkah
description: Haloumi is the king of cheeses, but add a golden coating and a drizzle of honey and it’s beyond belief! These gorgeous morsels are served on a robust autumn salad of dukkah roasted pumpkin, fresh veggies and vibrant mint for a seasonal and satisfying delight.
